title: Pset_DistributionPortPHistoryCable
description: Log of electrical activity attached to an instance of IfcPerformanceHistory having an assigned IfcDistributionPort of type CABLE.

DataTransmitted.title: DataTransmitted
DataTransmitted.description: For data ports, captures log of data transmitted.  The LIST at IfcTimeSeriesValue.Values may split out data according to Pset_DistributionPortTypeCable.Protocols.

DataReceived.title: DataReceived
DataReceived.description: For data ports, captures log of data received.  The LIST at IfcTimeSeriesValue.Values may split out data according to Pset_DistributionPortTypeCable.Protocols.
